         <h1 property="name" id="wb-cont" class="gc-thickline">Clean economy investment tax credits (ITCs) </h1>
         <p class="pagetag">Information to help your business get a credit for investing in either carbon capture and storage, or clean technology property.</p>
        
         <h2 class="wb-inv">Services and information</h2>
         <h2>Available ITCs</h2>
