                  <h3 class="h5"><a href="https://cra-proto.github.io/clean-economy/subway/ccus-index.html">Carbon Capture, Utilization, and Storage (CCUS) </a></h3>
                  <p>Investments in technologies that capture CO<sub>2</sub> emissions to either store or use in industry</p>
               </section>
            </div>
            <!-- 2 -->
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <section>
 <h3 class="h5"><a href="https://cra-proto.github.io/clean-economy/ct-subway/ct-index-alt.html">Clean Technology (CT)</a></h3>
                  <p>Investments of capital in the adoption and operations of new clean technology property in Canada</p>
               </section>
            </div>
         </div>
  
